## ✅ `ingredient_catalog_content.js`

> 📋 À utiliser sur la **page du catalogue** (liste des ingrédients)  
> 📦 Extrait tous les ingrédients visibles avec catégories

```javascript
function extractIngredientsData() {
    var results = [];
    var blocks = document.querySelectorAll(".ingredient-card, .ingredient-block");
    blocks.forEach(function(card) {
        var name = card.querySelector(".name")?.innerText || "";
        var type = card.querySelector(".type")?.innerText || "";
        var img = card.querySelector("img")?.src || "";
        var link = card.querySelector("a")?.getAttribute("href") || "";
        if (name !== "") {
            results.push({
                name: name,
                type: type,
                img_url: img,
                link: link
            });
        }
    });
    return results;
}
```

